body:
I found python scripts in the introductory tensorflow download documents
(which also include scripts for the iris classification problem used to
describe estimators) for MNIST in the directory
\TensorFlow_models-master\models-master\official\mnist. Are there any
accompanying materials on the Tensorflow website that describe the code in
the dataset.py and mnist.py scripts found in this folder?

Thank you.
